<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5097291>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Molgula tzetlini. A, specimen opened along ventral midline, branchial sac removed (KBPIG 1066/8); B, body removed from the test (KBPIG 725/6); C, right gonad and renal sac (KBPIG 700/3); D, gut loop and left gonad of juvenile specimen (KBPIG 723/5)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5097291/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

